### Task Service - Manual Testing Requests

### Environment Configuration
### Using local environment: http://localhost:8080/
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

### Create a new task
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "id": "task-001",
  "name": "Implement authentication",
  "description": "Add JWT-based authentication to the API",
  "status": "TODO"
}

### Create another task
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "id": "task-002",
  "name": "Setup database",
  "description": "Configure MongoDB connection for production",
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

### Create a third task
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "id": "task-003",
  "name": "Write unit tests",
  "description": "Add comprehensive test coverage for task service",
  "status": "DONE"
}

### Get task by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/task-001
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Get another task
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/task-002
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Update task - change status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/task-001
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
}

### Update task - change name and description
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/task-002
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Setup database - UPDATED",
  "description": "Configure MongoDB connection for both production and staging environments"
}

### Update task - complete task
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/task-001
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Implement authentication",
  "description": "Add JWT-based authentication to the API - COMPLETED",
  "status": "DONE"
}

### Update task - partial update (only status)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/tasks/task-003
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "ARCHIVED"
}

